{"id":270278,"type":3,"name":"NIGHTS BEFORE NIGHT","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/6d/08/270278_KKkw6.jpg","summary":"10年の夜を解く、救済。\r\n『MODS』本当の完結。\r\n元ヤクザでゲイ向けデリヘル「Rain」のオーナー・春は、一条組組長の息子である雪鷹を自宅で預かり、謹慎させることになる。\r\n暴力沙汰を起こす問題児の雪鷹は、春の想い人で今は亡きヤクザ・一条時雨の腹違いの弟だった。時雨の死に囚われながら不眠を患う春は、性格は真逆だが、時雨と似た相貌の雪鷹にしだいに翻弄されていき……。","info":"<li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/3878\">野島裕史</a> / <a href=\"/person/4976\">小野友樹</a> / <a href=\"/person/3822\">森川智之</a> / <a href=\"/person/14604\">斉藤壮馬</a> / <a href=\"/person/10525\">櫻井トオル</a> / <a href=\"/person/22599\">益山武明</a> / <a href=\"/person/4968\">坪井智浩</a> / <a href=\"/person/3998\">中博史</a> / <a href=\"/person/29132\">福原かつみ</a> / <a href=\"/person/25025\">石井未紗</a> / <a href=\"/person/29812\">清水はる香</a></li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2018-12-29</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥ 5,292</li><li><span>播放时长: </span>52分36秒＋64分39秒</li><li><span>碟片数量: </span>2</li><li><span>原作: </span>ナツメカズキ</li><li><span>厂牌: </span>marble records</li>","collection":{"collect":2,"doing":1,"on_hold":2},"tags":[{"name":"2018","count":2},{"name":"BLCD","count":2},{"name":"漫画改","count":1},{"name":"BLドラマCD","count":1},{"name":"小野友樹","count":1},{"name":"BLドラマ","count":1},{"name":"野島裕史","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":10525,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c4/05/10525_prsn_LlL54.jpg","name":"樱井透","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":14604,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8c/e3/14604_prsn_kRPr7.jpg","name":"齐藤壮马","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":3822,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e1/d8/3822_prsn_E2Q2J.jpg","name":"森川智之","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":22599,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/af/4b/22599_prsn_LIzLd.jpg","name":"益山武明","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":4968,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a4/82/4968_seiyu_anidb.jpg","name":"坪井智浩","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":25025,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/97/cd/25025_prsn_NZuxa.jpg","name":"石井未纱","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":29132,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/73/30/29132_prsn_8A6S8.jpg","name":"福原克己","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":3998,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f6/c6/3998_prsn_YobUg.jpg","name":"